Package org.stormdev.authlib.json.response

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientAuthResponse
    The response from the server for clientDualAuth.
    LoginInfoResponse
    The response from the server for retrieving login info
    LoginRequestResponse
    The response from the server for trying to login a user
    ServerAuthResponse
    The response from the server from serverDualAuth, if successful contains the account and session details except the SessionID
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ClientAuthError
    The possible errors for when clientDualAuth fails
    LoginInfoError
    All the possible errors from a LoginInfo request
    LoginRequestError
    All possible errors for logging into StormDev accounts
    ServerAuthError
    All possible errors for serverAuths
